Mother.

292
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:21,559
I don't have much appetite.

293
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:22,799
Please enjoy dinner.

294
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:30,080
I don't feel like eating either.

295
00:14:30,544 --> 00:14:31,920
Please enjoy the food.

296
00:14:41,279 --> 00:14:43,279
Though Siyan survived the plane crash,

297
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:45,000
I somehow feel that

298
00:14:45,639 --> 00:14:46,559
the two of them

299
00:14:46,648 --> 00:14:48,280
are not getting along well.

300
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:56,240
What's on your mind?

301
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:58,360
I'm thinking about

302
00:14:59,888 --> 00:15:01,480
when I should tell Father everything.

303
00:15:02,520 --> 00:15:03,632
If this keeps dragging on,

304
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,600
when will it ever end?

305
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:07,960
Aren't you afraid

306
00:15:08,160 --> 00:15:09,360
he'll kick you out of the house

307
00:15:09,759 --> 00:15:11,320
once you tell him?

308
00:15:13,159 --> 00:15:13,919
Then what?

309
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:16,039
If I end up homeless,

310
00:15:17,192 --> 00:15:18,256
please take me in.

311
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:23,320
Wouldn't that be expensive?

312
00:15:23,679 --> 00:15:24,759
I have to think about it.

313
00:15:24,904 --> 00:15:26,480
No at all. I'm easy to feed.

314
00:15:27,279 --> 00:15:27,840
Really?

315
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:28,840
Yeah.

316
00:15:34,728 --> 00:15:35,280
Mother.

317
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:40,320
I know it's my fault

318
00:15:41,039 --> 00:15:42,639
that you can't date openly.

319
00:15:43,919 --> 00:15:44,559
But please

320
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,039
give me a little more time.

321
00:15:46,120 --> 00:15:48,039
I'll confess to Master.

322
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:50,879
I understand, Mother.

323
00:15:51,919 --> 00:15:52,440
Siyan,

324
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:54,720
will you

325
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:56,440
still accept me as your mother?

326
00:15:57,039 --> 00:15:58,200
You'll always be my mother.

327
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:02,000
Chuning.

328
00:16:03,759 --> 00:16:04,480
Mrs. Lu.

329
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:06,440
I'm sorry.

330
00:16:18,300 --> 00:16:20,540
(Punish Evil, Uphold Justice)

331
00:16:25,919 --> 00:16:27,200
Congratulations, Chief Shen.

332
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:28,759
You've become

333
00:16:28,879 --> 00:16:31,600
a hero of justice to the people.

334
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:37,919
Out with it.

335
00:16:38,919 --> 00:16:40,039
What did you come here for?

336
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:43,440
I want you to kill Lu Siyan.

337
00:16:44,159 --> 00:16:45,360
Mr. Gao is dead,

338
00:16:45,759 --> 00:16:47,039
and Lu Siyan abandoned you.

339
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:49,440
Do you think

340
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:50,639
you're useful

341
00:16:51,759 --> 00:16:53,159
to me now?

342
00:16:53,480 --> 00:16:55,039
You used me and hung me out to dry?

343
00:17:00,679 --> 00:17:01,440
I'm discarding

344
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:03,159
a worthless pawn.

345
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:08,839
You bribed the mechanic
in the flight academy

346
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:11,680
to tamper with the aircraft
Lu Siyan was in, didn't you?

347
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:14,960
Also, you made me take the blame
for that sachet.

348
00:17:18,519 --> 00:17:19,359
Go on.

349
00:17:21,359 --> 00:17:22,559
Keep talking.

350
00:17:23,799 --> 00:17:25,200
The boxes Mr. Gao had

351
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:26,960
didn't contain porcelain.

352
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,880
You swapped the girls out beforehand

353
00:17:29,119 --> 00:17:31,039
to scheme against Lin Chuning
and Lu Siyan.

354
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,440
Poor Mr. Gao,

355
00:17:34,799 --> 00:17:35,880
he died without even knowing

356
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:38,640
he was your scapegoat.

357
00:17:43,580 --> 00:17:45,060
(Account Book)

358
00:17:46,559 --> 00:17:47,359
What is this?

359
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:49,519
I'm pledging my loyalty to you.

360
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:59,039
This is Mr. Gao's account book.

361
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:01,920
If you wish to build
your own Wenrou Lounge,

362
00:18:02,039 --> 00:18:03,000
you'll need this.

363
00:18:11,039 --> 00:18:12,599
I'm just a poor, helpless woman

364
00:18:13,039 --> 00:18:15,240
who's trying to look for someone
to cling to.

365
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:23,240
Well.

366
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:28,119
Please take pity on me, Chief Shen.

367
00:18:57,079 --> 00:18:58,200
This dress...

368
00:18:59,039 --> 00:18:59,640
Do you like it?

369
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:04,640
I had it made for you.

370
00:19:07,079 --> 00:19:08,720
I like anything you pick.

371
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,200
I'll take you somewhere.

372
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:30,599
Where?

373
00:19:31,559 --> 00:19:32,720
You'll see.

374
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:34,559
All right.

375
00:19:59,039 --> 00:20:00,200
Here. Feet up.

376
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:01,400
Careful.

377
00:20:01,839 --> 00:20:02,759
Take it slow.

378
00:20:08,280 --> 00:20:08,776
All right.

379
00:20:09,280 --> 00:20:09,744
Here we are.

380
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:20,799
Okay.

381
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:36,799
Hold this.

382
00:20:41,559 --> 00:20:44,519
Chuning,
there's something I want to say.

383
00:20:45,559 --> 00:20:47,640
I fell for you at first sight.

384
00:20:48,039 --> 00:20:49,240
But I didn't know

385
00:20:49,319 --> 00:20:50,440
what love was.

386
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:52,519
So after going through ups and downs,

387
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:55,599
and when I realized
I had truly loved you,

388
00:20:56,280 --> 00:20:57,480
I found out you were my sister.

389
00:20:58,032 --> 00:20:59,848
I don't think anything could be worse

390
00:21:00,599 --> 00:21:02,400
than that.

391
00:21:03,079 --> 00:21:04,039
That's when I knew

392
00:21:04,960 --> 00:21:05,799
my feelings for you

393
00:21:06,759 --> 00:21:08,039
run so deep.

394
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:11,000
Otherwise, even after losing

395
00:21:12,119 --> 00:21:13,160
all my memories,

396
00:21:14,559 --> 00:21:17,319
I wouldn't have remembered
that I love you.

397
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,519
After everything we went through,

398
00:21:22,039 --> 00:21:23,319
I'm going to be brave once again.

399
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:30,279
Chuning.

400
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:37,160
Will you

401
00:21:40,039 --> 00:21:40,960
marry me?

402
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:54,519
No, I won't.

403
00:22:13,260 --> 00:22:16,170
♪Barging into the sea
that bears your name♪

404
00:22:16,580 --> 00:22:19,030
♪Swimming to the end with loneliness♪

405
00:22:19,150 --> 00:22:22,420
♪Going against the current
and over the reef traps♪

406
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:25,640
♪Clearing the fog
just to get close to you♪

407
00:22:26,620 --> 00:22:29,390
♪Pushing away
the gravel hidden beneath the seaweed♪

408
00:22:29,950 --> 00:22:32,360
♪Wandering near your heart♪

409
00:22:32,460 --> 00:22:35,990
♪I imagined
our encounter countless times♪

410
00:22:36,170 --> 00:22:38,990
♪So close, yet out of reach♪

411
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:45,050
♪Keeping
all this lonely courage to myself♪

412
00:22:46,210 --> 00:22:52,380
♪I was never part of your world♪

413
00:22:52,470 --> 00:22:56,000
♪If your silhouette
was etched upon the sea♪

414
00:22:56,190 --> 00:22:59,050
♪The sky as your wedding dress♪

415
00:22:59,110 --> 00:23:02,640
♪Turn me into a cloud♪

416
