437
00:24:39,120 --> 00:24:42,860
♪If the sea didn't wait
for the evening breeze♪

438
00:24:42,930 --> 00:24:45,730
♪And swim with me to you♪

439
00:24:45,780 --> 00:24:49,320
♪I'd become♪

440
00:24:49,470 --> 00:24:52,380
♪A whale
who forever keeps the sea company♪

441
